ito the `eth1` IP address of Magma access gateway via DNS. Modify your		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
irouter's DNS settings to hijack the IP of `acs.freedomfi.com` to the `eth1`		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
